{"tid":656854,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【割地兩檢】何君堯開會打閃燈拍片 做鬼臉手勢懶理投訴","createTime":"2018-05-07T14:47:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-08T01:12:44.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"b51f9dcdeecb006edebcd7e5cfd2a9a73da4377a","tid":656854,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T14:47:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180507/58163432?_ga=2.33736417.1769260499.1525579676-581282530.1504247435\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180507%2F58163432%3F_ga%3D2.33736417.1769260499.1525579676-581282530.1504247435&d=YMKMvWjbSZ2l7e2QC27ucv%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=e2234422\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180507%2F58163432%3F_ga%3D2.33736417.1769260499.1525579676-581282530.1504247435&h=a7b1bc1c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180507/58163432?_ga=2.33736417.1769260499.1525579676-581282530.1504247435</a><br />\n<br />\n【割地兩檢】何君堯開會打閃燈拍片 做鬼臉手勢懶理投訴<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【新增短片】<br />\n<br />\n立法會一地兩檢條例草案委員會下午復會後，主席葉劉淑儀辯稱表決前，未聞有議員就一併表決提出反對，並指及後會續條修正案表決。但民主派對葉劉隨意「搬龍門」做法不滿，並在位上爭論，葉劉再提出暫停會議3分鐘。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n葉劉再次復會後，葉劉指知道有議員不同意一併就陳志全4項修正案作表決，提出就是否重新逐一投票作投票，即因建制派的反對票較多而遭否決。委員會隨後就各條修正案逐一表決，亦無如其他大會會議的記名表決般「響鐘」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n在表決修正案期間，民主派朱凱廸突衝向主席位置，遭保安阻止，大部分民主派議員站立，手持標語，並高叫「割地兩檢違憲」。葉劉未有理會民主派議員抗議，續就修正案進行表決。會議室內有近30名保安駐守，築成人牆防止泛民議員走近主席台。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n與此同時，建制派何君堯用手機並開動閃光燈拍攝、在facebook做live，民主派即要求葉劉處理，何君堯卻以鬼臉手勢回應。陳志全隨即上前爭論，葉劉終要求何停止攝錄。<br />\n葉劉在完成表決修正案後，指會於5月25日向內務委員會提出一地兩檢草案，並提出於6月6日恢復二讀。委員會最終30票贊成、13票反對、1票棄權，通過於6月6日在大會二讀草案。葉劉隨即宣布散會。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n葉劉在完成表決離開時，運房局長陳帆等官員即上前與她握手。葉劉其後指自己「喉嚨痛」，要小休一會再見傳媒。  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180507/large/1525686452_8f0c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180507%2Flarge%2F1525686452_8f0c.jpg&h=a51a4ffe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n何君堯用手機並開動閃光燈拍攝，民主派即要求委員會主席葉劉處理，何卻以鬼臉手勢回應。（王心義攝）<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180507/large/1525686538_53c7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180507%2Flarge%2F1525686538_53c7.jpg&h=d0663902&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n王心義攝<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180507/large/1525686552_785e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180507%2Flarge%2F1525686552_785e.jpg&h=a43c9ae3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n朱永倫攝"},{"pid":"ec697a6cd3aa4c457744376dd4462daa1ba303a6","tid":656854,"uid":174648,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T15:11:10.000Z","msg":"個樣幾鬼馬，幾純真，咁咪幾好，搞咁多屎忽鬼野為咩?"},{"pid":"808ec8b565a952a8feba1b94e07541756e68001b","tid":656854,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T00:34:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 垃圾做議員"},{"pid":"f909fe9afc2b6e492cab81297d66b71920bce6c0","tid":656854,"uid":143499,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T00:44:57.000Z","msg":"屌你老母戇鳩都可以做議員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c198727eda010d3fa3e8ba3a282dd2fa22186330","tid":656854,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T00:52:35.000Z","msg":"泛民打手LIKLN<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/08/085234_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F08%2F085234_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=f1bd0b4e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3b64f6d458a5c5d9dbd11d16e4fe86a35848660b","tid":656854,"uid":163750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T01:01:43.000Z","msg":"屌 仲細咩 成個老坑小學雞咁 見到都想嘔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c39b2e8fb77c692fe0e4c18fa265b553b86b7c62","tid":656854,"uid":93479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T01:12:44.000Z","msg":"立法局 : 李鵬飛，李柱銘，鄧蓮如<br />\n立法會 : 何君堯，葉劉，黃國興，鍾樹根，蔣云"}]}